**Location**: `/c/Users/johnm/modular apartment planner/src/three/viewer/buildPreviewObjects.js`

Each fixture has a custom builder function that constructs detailed 3D geometry:

- **`buildKitchenTopFixture`** (lines 260-280): Cabinet body + countertop + stovetop + 4 burners (cylinders) + sink
- **`buildToiletFixture`** (lines 282-297): Cistern box + cistern cap + bowl outer/inner + seat rim (all cylinders except boxes)
- **`buildLavatoryFixture`** (lines 299-319): Pedestal column + base + basin outer/inner/rim (cylinders) + faucet stem/spout
- **`buildTableFixture`** (lines 321-346): Tabletop + aprons + 4 legs (cylinders)
- **`buildTvFixture`** (lines 348-360): Screen panel + bezels + stand neck + stand base
